content:
IMPRESSION: A sequence of movements, like a dance. Instructions provided, as though from a teacher on the subject. I perform each movement in response:

Breathe in through the head (witness ‘energy’ coming into the head);

Exhale through the heart (witness ‘energy’ releasing from the sternum);

Breathe in through the gut (dantien);

Exhale through the heart;

Breathe into the heart;

Exhale from the heart.

REFLECTION: This is a process that can be used to filter + purify input.

This is an invitation. Use + share this process.
